====Verb====
'''voorkomen''' (''stress on "voor"'')
# To [[exist]]; to [[occur]].
#: ''Deze soort komt niet voor in Afrika.'' &mdash; This species doesn't occur in Africa.
# To [[appear]].
# To [[get]] [[ahead]]; to [[draw]] ahead.

